room_title: Escape room "(Wolf/Ram/Devil) The Mascot Rescue" by Escape on Purpose in Raleigh - Durham
review: This was such a good escape room! The best staff and a well thought-out room. definitely will be coming back to try the other ones!

room_title: Escape room "(Wolf/Ram/Devil) The Mascot Rescue" by Escape on Purpose in Raleigh - Durham
review: Great time at Escape on Purpose. We did the Mascot Rescue Room. We were able to break out the Blue Devil just in time!

room_title: Escape room "(Wolf/Ram/Devil) The Mascot Rescue" by Escape on Purpose in Raleigh - Durham
review: Did the Mascot room for my birthday - it was wonderfully fun! I love that escaping a room also helps a local nonprofit. Owners are insanely nice!
